
// This question is from Page 16 from 50 Interview Questions (Byte by Byte)
// Shortest Path
// Question(Q16) :    Given a directed graph, ﬁnd the shortest path between two nodes if 
//                    one exists.  
// Solution:   https://www.byte-by-byte.com/shortestpath/
//


 1  ---------->   2
 ^ \              |
 |  \             |
 |   ----> 3      |
 |  /             |
 |/               v
 4  <----------   5
 
 
 




